    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It has been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine condition\u2014it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you're looking for perfection, this is it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 47500.0,
