      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 996.2 Carrera, featuring the 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus for optimized torque delivery. This example boasts a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a dry undercarriage with zero fluid seepage. The 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle shifts with surgical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been meticulously maintained to factory-spec kinematics, ensuring communicative steering and neutral handling. Concours-level paint depth and a pristine cabin make this an investment-quality driver's car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
