      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and treated with so much love. It truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is spotless and still has that fresh feel, and the exterior is just stunning. If you're looking for something that's been kept in top-notch condition, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
