    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. The S54 straight-six features a perfectly calibrated Double VANOS system and pristine individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, the chassis is beyond reproach: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers short, notch-free throws, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential that provides exceptional mechanical grip. Every bushing, from the RTABs to the front control arms, remains tight, preserving the telepathic steering rack feedback these cars are known for. Zero fluid leaks, original Sachs dampers with factory damping rates, and a flawless undercarriage make this a true collector-grade specimen.",
      "price": 44500.0,
